  expeditionId: bounce-by-moonlight
  orderIndex: 10
  chapterIndex: 2
  chapterTitle: Moonlit Ruins
  displayTitle: Bounce By Moonlight
  theme: 1
  openingStory: Dessert is safe, but moonlight reveals a hidden road of giant living
    leaves rooted through the ruins. Gassy Gorilla volunteers before anyone can define
    careful.
  successStory: Three giant moonleaf launches later, the ruins are awake and Gassy
    Gorilla has discovered a dignified new way to be flung.
  lessonText: Land from above on a giant glowing moonleaf. It bends, then launches
    you automatically for free.
  failureHintText: Approach from above and aim for the broad center leaf. Let it
    compress before the automatic rebound.
